divs: sighting detailsi was standing in front of my home overlooking the city where i live and as i was looking directly overhead , while sheilding my eyes from the city light, i observed a object that apeared to be shaped like a oval solid\intertube without a hole in the center, hence solid. it was silent fast dull red object traveling south to north seen over el cajon moving toward el capitan resivoir where it disapeared from my view when trying to point out object to my father nearby. there were 2 airplane nearby... 1 oon a short approach to gilespie field, over el cajon and turning from downwind (east heading and turning north ) to base before turning for final aproach on runway 27 left, the 2nd airplane was on long a long final aproach and was inbound over alpine crest heading west on aproach on 27 right. the object passed between and above the 2 aircraft.
